{"tid":1771094,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【緊急】選戰未完，保皇狗一年一度蛇齌餅粽就緒","createTime":"2019-12-05T15:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T07:49:56.000Z","uid":36073,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8774e6eef4ee4ceeca1e44ea031560d04f62e1e9","tid":1771094,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:02:32.000Z","msg":"當我哋光復咗區議會，候任議員要待2020年1月1日先正式上任。保皇狗當然唔認輸，執返啲沙都要繼續蛇齌餅粽，靠一個logo嚟洗你老母老豆個腦，係乜嘢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係月曆呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjnDtXo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjnDtXo.png&h=ba39e5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條陳曼琪個契仔已經準備好 1300 個月曆喺來年用民賤聯個logo洗你腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55zROXU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55zROXU.png&h=485287b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1300個月曆，即係代表我哋有可能來年立法會會輸咗1300張票去俾保皇狗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，我要每一個連登仔，當你見到保皇黨月曆派街，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請立即排隊為屋企兩老攞返份，仲要順便叫埋一齊去攞多幾份呀</span></span><br />\n之後要點做，大家都明的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋所有候任區議員，一定要參考保皇黨做法，滲透社區每一個角落，一份月曆可以影響到好多架。無論如何，一定要繼續爭取任何一張可能嘅選票呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f6036d2234b16f6982b432aa606940487bdb32","tid":1771094,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fc8764dfd915f0d7872ddea6872abeaa6c6aed","tid":1771094,"uid":59815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:12:58.000Z","m